Meet me later,
I have to rush, dear

1087
01:09:12,081 --> 01:09:14,755
It's for my man
I dolled up and came here

1088
01:09:14,884 --> 01:09:17,160
He slid this ornament into me

1089
01:09:17,453 --> 01:09:20,059
A mirror, quick,
to see the glow he 'll see...

1090
01:09:20,156 --> 01:09:21,931
Let me go to him

1091
01:09:23,092 --> 01:09:25,402
Let me go please

1092
01:09:25,761 --> 01:09:27,866
Have to go now

1093
01:09:28,731 --> 01:09:31,007
Need to go now

1094
01:09:31,534 --> 01:09:33,013
Let me go now

1095
01:09:33,736 --> 01:09:36,080
Don't flirt and tease

1096
01:09:36,739 --> 01:09:38,446
Let go of me

1097
01:09:39,408 --> 01:09:42,787
Release me please

1098
01:09:43,579 --> 01:09:45,855
I'm going now

1099
01:09:47,183 --> 01:09:50,460
Let me go now

1100
01:09:52,821 --> 01:09:54,892
Let me go to her

1101
01:09:55,891 --> 01:09:58,997
Alright Rusy,
here's Rs. 150,000

1102
01:10:00,429 --> 01:10:02,500
Before the Press gets here,
take the car away

1103
01:10:03,199 --> 01:10:04,200
Thank you

1104
01:11:19,775 --> 01:11:21,118
Mohan

1105
01:11:22,578 --> 01:11:25,252
How much does a
Ferrari cost?

1106
01:11:26,048 --> 01:11:27,049
I'll tell you

1107
01:11:27,683 --> 01:11:29,685
If you sell that hole
you call home...

1108
01:11:30,185 --> 01:11:33,029
to three people,
over three years...

1109
01:11:33,789 --> 01:11:35,826
you still won't get a Ferrari tire

1110
01:11:36,625 --> 01:11:38,127
Don't fib

1111
01:11:38,761 --> 01:11:40,638
It has just two seats

1112
01:11:41,096 --> 01:11:43,098
No seats in the back

1113
01:11:43,766 --> 01:11:45,643
A scooter also has two seats

1114
01:11:45,934 --> 01:11:47,743
A Ferrari also has two seats

1115
01:11:48,304 --> 01:11:52,150
How much extra can
two wheels cost?

1116
01:11:54,310 --> 01:11:57,086
4... 5000?

1117
01:11:57,913 --> 01:12:00,120
Hello?

1118
01:12:00,849 --> 01:12:02,055
Good morning, ma'am

1119
01:12:02,618 --> 01:12:04,325
Yes ma'am. OK ma'am

1120
01:12:04,853 --> 01:12:05,923
Have a good day

1121
01:12:06,722 --> 01:12:07,860
What's the matter, Mohan?

1122
01:12:08,157 --> 01:12:11,138
That was Mrs. Tendulkar.
Boss is coming back

1123
01:12:11,293 --> 01:12:12,966
I'm off to my village

1124
01:12:12,995 --> 01:12:13,628
Wait

1125
01:12:13,629 --> 01:12:15,609
Tell the cops
I committed suicide

1126
01:12:15,764 --> 01:12:18,870
And my body is in
Shamshu's furnace

1127
01:12:19,034 --> 01:12:20,104
Wait, calm down

1128
01:12:20,269 --> 01:12:22,772
We have some time.
I have a plan. C'mon

1129
01:12:22,971 --> 01:12:24,143
Leave me out of it

1130
01:12:24,273 --> 01:12:26,753
Boss is back tomorrow night,
don't worry

1131
01:12:27,109 --> 01:12:27,951
Come with me

1132
01:12:31,680 --> 01:12:32,351
Mohan

1133
01:12:33,082 --> 01:12:33,992
Police

1134
01:12:34,216 --> 01:12:35,320
Run

1135
01:12:35,718 --> 01:12:36,753
Run!

1136
01:12:36,952 --> 01:12:37,930
C'mon, hurry

1137
01:12:38,153 --> 01:12:39,821
Mohan, wait for me.
My helmet

1138
01:12:39,822 --> 01:12:43,031
Put it on. Use your head

1139
01:13:01,610 --> 01:13:03,055
Mohan

1140
01:13:06,882 --> 01:13:09,362
Mohan, I can hear
the sound of the Ferrari

1141
01:13:09,852 --> 01:13:11,092
You're going mad. Run

1142
01:13:30,372 --> 01:13:33,910
Rustom Behram Deboo,
Transport Office

1143
01:13:35,077 --> 01:13:36,852
Sir, why's the police
here today?

1144
01:13:37,146 --> 01:13:39,183
The Ganesh festival
and Sachin's century...

1145
01:13:39,415 --> 01:13:41,088
That's when the police
works overtime

1146
01:13:41,683 --> 01:13:42,957
Just a precaution
- OK

1147
01:13:43,952 --> 01:13:44,862
Not starting?

1148
01:13:45,020 --> 01:13:46,693
It'll start, sir

1149
01:13:47,356 --> 01:13:48,357
Listen, try this

1150
01:13:48,757 --> 01:13:50,202
Run it down the slope
in neutral

1151
01:13:50,692 --> 01:13:52,763
Then slip it into 2nd gear.
It'll start

1152
01:13:53,128 --> 01:13:53,765
OK...

1153
01:13:53,862 --> 01:13:55,034
Get on the slope

1154
01:13:55,264 --> 01:13:56,743
In neutral?
- Yes

1155
01:13:56,899 --> 01:13:59,106
Keep it in neutral.
Now put it into 2nd gear

1156
01:13:59,301 --> 01:14:00,405
There, it started

1157
01:14:06,842 --> 01:14:08,321
Rustom, hold on

1158
01:14:09,011 --> 01:14:10,115
Help me with this

1159
01:14:10,312 --> 01:14:11,985
Got to nab this red car

1160
01:14:15,250 --> 01:14:16,388
Yes sir...

1161
01:14:32,701 --> 01:14:33,304
Hello?

1162
01:14:33,769 --> 01:14:36,909
Rusy, where are you?
It's morning

1163
01:14:37,272 --> 01:14:38,216
Where were you?

1164
01:14:39,107 --> 01:14:42,145
Papa, something terrible
has happened

1165
01:14:43,345 --> 01:14:45,052
What... You had an accident?

1166
01:14:46,315 --> 01:14:49,762
Papa, I stole Sachin's Ferrari

1167
01:14:52,221 --> 01:14:54,827
You crazy?
I was fooling with you

1168
01:14:55,224 --> 01:14:56,294
Where's the car?

1169
01:14:57,793 --> 01:15:01,036
The car's being towed away

1170
01:15:01,430 --> 01:15:04,309
Now do as I say.
Come straight home

1171
01:15:04,466 --> 01:15:05,308
Wear your helmet

1172
01:15:05,434 --> 01:15:07,846
Hide your face from the cops

1173
01:15:08,070 --> 01:15:09,737
Something really terrible
happened, Papa

1174
01:15:09,738 --> 01:15:11,046
What now?

1175
01:15:12,941 --> 01:15:15,148
Papa, I left Rs.150,000
in the car

1176
01:15:17,913 --> 01:15:20,120
Kayo can't go to Lord's, Papa

1177
01:15:22,885 --> 01:15:24,091
Kayo... Lord's...

1178
01:15:42,538 --> 01:15:46,213
Pawar, prepare that report.
I'm leaving

1179
01:15:46,475 --> 01:15:47,215
C'mon Jadhav

1180
01:15:48,176 --> 01:15:49,154
Jadhav, slow down

1181
01:15:49,611 --> 01:15:53,058
Stop, I said

1182
01:15:54,850 --> 01:15:58,559
Inspector Mhatre,
what have you brought in?

1183
01:15:59,121 --> 01:16:01,601
It's called a car.
Has four wheels...

1184
01:16:01,790 --> 01:16:03,929
Sir, this is no car.
It's a celestial chariot

1185
01:16:04,092 --> 01:16:05,730
The chariot of my God

1186
01:16:05,928 --> 01:16:08,272
It's Sachin Tendulkar's Ferrari

1187
01:16:08,630 --> 01:16:10,507
But your God parked
in a No Parking zone

1188
01:16:10,666 --> 01:16:13,510
Will my God come
to get his car, sir?

1189
01:16:13,702 --> 01:16:15,613
Whether it's your God
or his driver...

1190
01:16:15,771 --> 01:16:18,115
don't release the car
without taking the fine

1191
01:16:18,540 --> 01:16:21,146
Don't worry, sir.
I'll watch over this car

1192
01:16:24,112 --> 01:16:25,113
0 Lord, thank you

1193
01:16:34,590 --> 01:16:37,196
There's the Ferrari

1194
01:16:40,596 --> 01:16:42,940
Looking good, Pakya

1195
01:16:43,966 --> 01:16:45,912
But the Ferrari can't be seen

1196
01:16:46,134 --> 01:16:48,546
Where is the Ferrari?

1197
01:16:48,737 --> 01:16:50,683
Look for it

1198
01:16:52,708 --> 01:16:53,948
Go to the next one

1199
01:16:54,076 --> 01:16:55,680
It's covered with flowers

1200
01:16:55,844 --> 01:16:57,551
Is it a Ferrari
or a humble taxi?

1201
01:16:57,779 --> 01:17:01,591
Pakya, your dad's fooled you

1202
01:17:01,984 --> 01:17:05,329
His dad fooled him

1203
01:17:05,687 --> 01:17:06,722
How many done, Babbu didi?

1204
01:17:06,922 --> 01:17:08,959
180 couples done, 20 to go

1205
01:17:09,157 --> 01:17:10,135
20...

1206
01:17:10,258 --> 01:17:11,601
You. Come here

1207
01:17:11,760 --> 01:17:13,103
Married?
- Yes sir

1208
01:17:13,228 --> 01:17:14,332
What was the hurry?

1209
01:17:14,796 --> 01:17:15,934
Never mind

1210
01:17:16,164 --> 01:17:17,871
Get your wife
and get re-married

1211
01:17:18,033 --> 01:17:19,273
But sir...
- If she objects...

1212
01:17:19,668 --> 01:17:21,773
tell her you're
renewing your vows

1213
01:17:21,803 --> 01:17:24,010
She'll be thrilled.
Run, now

1214
01:17:24,206 --> 01:17:25,776
That makes 181 couples

1215
01:17:25,974 --> 01:17:26,952
Give me a minute

1216
01:17:28,810 --> 01:17:30,011
What's this?
- What's what?

1217
01:17:30,012 --> 01:17:31,320
What's this, Babbu didi?

1218
01:17:31,847 --> 01:17:33,793
Who told you to use
so many flowers?

1219
01:17:33,949 --> 01:17:35,587
Who does that to a Ferrari?

1220
01:17:35,717 --> 01:17:38,288
It's a wedding car -
it must have flowers

1221
01:17:38,687 --> 01:17:40,257
You're Mr. Mandke's
son, no less

1222
01:17:40,689 --> 01:17:42,691
If there were fewer flowers,
people would gossip

1223
01:17:42,824 --> 01:17:43,962
They'd call us stingy

1224
01:17:44,092 --> 01:17:45,366
They're gossiping now

1225
01:17:45,761 --> 01:17:47,604
Saying it's not a Ferrari
under the flowers...

1226
01:17:47,729 --> 01:17:48,969
it's an ordinary taxi

1227
01:17:49,264 --> 01:17:50,709
People will say anything

1228
01:17:50,866 --> 01:17:53,142
You know the truth.
You know it's a Ferrari

1229
01:17:53,602 --> 01:17:56,981
Walk the path of truth, son.
It's useful in the long run

1230
01:17:57,105 --> 01:17:58,641
You wronged me, Babbu didi

1231
01:17:58,674 --> 01:17:59,345
C'mon now...

1232
01:17:59,675 --> 01:18:01,882
You committed a fraud

1233
01:18:02,310 --> 01:18:04,256
Our deal is off

1234
01:18:04,713 --> 01:18:05,851
No compromise

1235
01:18:06,048 --> 01:18:08,289
At my wedding tomorrow,
I want the Ferrari

1236
01:18:08,750 --> 01:18:09,888
Without flowers on it

1237
01:18:12,888 --> 01:18:14,196
Go on, now

1238
01:18:14,690 --> 01:18:16,692
Told you to get an abortion

1239
01:18:16,892 --> 01:18:18,337
Look at what you produced

1240
01:18:18,727 --> 01:18:19,865
What kind of talk is that?

1241
01:18:20,262 --> 01:18:21,639
Mom...

1242
01:18:22,064 --> 01:18:24,271
What sort of guy did you marry?

1243
01:18:24,800 --> 01:18:26,867
If you had asked me,
I would've rejected him

1244
01:18:26,868 --> 01:18:28,074
Be quiet

1245
01:18:30,972 --> 01:18:32,974
You all go ahead

1246
01:18:33,108 --> 01:18:33,745
Pakya...

1247
01:18:35,010 --> 01:18:36,683
Don't say anything

1248
01:18:36,845 --> 01:18:37,845
Leave, I said

1249
01:18:37,846 --> 01:18:38,881
Going

1250
01:18:40,015 --> 01:18:41,961
Babbu didi, please handle this

1251
01:18:46,354 --> 01:18:49,130
The Press will not see
the Ferrari

1252
01:18:49,725 --> 01:18:50,795
That's final

1253
01:18:51,326 --> 01:18:54,068
That's my order

1254
01:18:54,930 --> 01:18:58,036
Then the Press will not see...

1255
01:18:58,934 --> 01:19:02,177
me wearing a number

1256
01:19:02,804 --> 01:19:03,805
That's my wish

1257
01:19:04,072 --> 01:19:07,408
You can't afford a wish,
you pipsqueak

1258
01:19:07,409 --> 01:19:09,013
Dad, no...

1259
01:19:10,278 --> 01:19:12,315
Don't mess with me, boy

1260
01:19:15,917 --> 01:19:19,763
Sir, couple no. 182

1261
01:19:22,891 --> 01:19:24,302
I'll see you at home

1262
01:19:28,730 --> 01:19:29,367
What happened?

1263
01:19:29,898 --> 01:19:31,104
Scram

1264
01:19:32,434 --> 01:19:34,311
I've always told you...

1265
01:19:34,469 --> 01:19:36,005
to stay away from cricket

1266
01:19:36,304 --> 01:19:38,375
It's made you into a thief now

1267
01:19:39,274 --> 01:19:41,049
The Great Gangster
of the Deboo family...

1268
01:19:41,143 --> 01:19:42,918
Rustom Behram Deboo

1269
01:19:43,145 --> 01:19:44,852
Papa, I have to
send Kayo to Lord's

1270
01:19:45,380 --> 01:19:47,917
Why are you so dense?

1271
01:19:48,283 --> 01:19:51,196
During recession in the
white man's land...

1272
01:19:51,219 --> 01:19:53,096
camps like this are invented

1273
01:19:53,221 --> 01:19:56,259
They look for gullible fools
like you, who fall for it

1274
01:19:56,424 --> 01:19:58,335
You want to go to prison?

1275
01:19:58,794 --> 01:20:02,207
In prison, hold a slate,
get your mug shots taken

1276
01:20:02,464 --> 01:20:04,102
Make your family famous

1277
01:20:04,399 --> 01:20:07,175
Cricket ruins you, I tell you

1278
01:20:09,104 --> 01:20:12,813
There're many dirty games
behind this sport

1279
01:20:13,074 --> 01:20:14,109
Answer this...

1280
01:20:14,309 --> 01:20:16,482
Who knows cricket best,
you or me?

1281
01:20:17,512 --> 01:20:18,456
Papa, I know...
- No, tell me...

1282
01:20:18,480 --> 01:20:20,926
who knows cricket best,
you or me?

1283
01:20:21,316 --> 01:20:23,193
Papa, I know some cricket too

1284
01:20:23,518 --> 01:20:24,929
I played well once

1285
01:20:25,086 --> 01:20:26,292
But you didn't let me play

1286
01:20:26,454 --> 01:20:28,024
Well, thank me for it

1287
01:20:28,323 --> 01:20:30,234
I saved you

1288
01:20:30,425 --> 01:20:31,904
Protected you

1289
01:20:31,993 --> 01:20:33,836
Papa, don't protect Kayo

1290
01:20:34,196 --> 01:20:36,005
Let him live his life

1291
01:20:36,531 --> 01:20:38,067
He's a gifted cricketer

1292
01:20:38,400 --> 01:20:39,538
He'll make you proud one day

1293
01:20:39,868 --> 01:20:42,371
That pint-sized rookie
a cricketer?

1294
01:20:42,804 --> 01:20:45,944
He knocks a ball in a sock
in the living room

1295
01:20:46,141 --> 01:20:48,052
That won't make him
a cricketer

1296
01:20:48,176 --> 01:20:49,814
Papa, you haven't
seen his game

1297
01:20:49,945 --> 01:20:51,322
He's captain of his team

1298
01:20:51,980 --> 01:20:55,427
In India, millions of kids
play cricket

1299
01:20:55,550 --> 01:20:58,224
From the city center,
if you hurl a pebble...

1300
01:20:58,353 --> 01:21:01,334
it'll land on a captain's head

1301
01:21:02,457 --> 01:21:03,094
Rusy

1302
01:21:03,291 --> 01:21:04,861
Remember this...

1303
01:21:05,126 --> 01:21:08,266
In a cricket team,
there are only eleven players

1304
01:21:09,030 --> 01:21:11,408
What of those who don't
make it to the team?

1305
01:21:11,933 --> 01:21:13,071
I'll tell you

1306
01:21:13,368 --> 01:21:15,905
They sit on a sofa,
stare at the

1307
01:21:16,004 --> 01:21:18,484
use a remote control,
and tuck into peanuts

1308
01:21:19,140 --> 01:21:23,418
You may as well put a
Kayo-sized sofa next to mine

1309
01:21:25,247 --> 01:21:27,193
Why are you destroying his life?

1310
01:21:27,349 --> 01:21:29,158
I'm not destroying his life

1311
01:21:29,417 --> 01:21:30,395
I'm helping him make it

1312
01:21:30,585 --> 01:21:33,589
You think he'll ever make it
to the top eleven?

1313
01:21:37,459 --> 01:21:38,597
No Papa

1314
01:21:40,595 --> 01:21:42,336
He's way ahead of the top eleven

1315
01:21:43,565 --> 01:21:45,306
No one is even close to him

1316
01:21:47,002 --> 01:21:48,072
Not even you

1317
01:21:49,070 --> 01:21:50,447
Know who you're talking to?

1318
01:21:52,474 --> 01:21:54,351
You're talking to
Behram Ardeshir Deboo

1319
01:21:55,443 --> 01:21:57,184
You know who you're talking to?

1320
01:22:11,626 --> 01:22:13,071
Papa, you were the bestest?

1321
01:22:13,395 --> 01:22:15,068
Bowl as many balls as you want

1322
01:22:15,964 --> 01:22:16,635
Just...

1323
01:22:18,133 --> 01:22:19,942
try and get him out

1324
01:22:27,175 --> 01:22:29,451
Kayo

1325
01:22:31,413 --> 01:22:32,084
Papa

1326
01:22:33,381 --> 01:22:34,257
Want to play a match?

1327
01:22:34,516 --> 01:22:35,324
A match?

1328
01:22:36,184 --> 01:22:36,992
Now?

1329
01:22:38,019 --> 01:22:39,123
With whom?

1330
01:22:49,631 --> 01:22:50,371
Papa?

1331
01:26:14,636 --> 01:26:15,876
He's asleep?

1332
01:26:17,138 --> 01:26:18,344
Yes Papa

1333
01:26:26,214 --> 01:26:27,852
Today's the selection?

1334
01:26:29,817 --> 01:26:31,125
Yes Papa

1335
01:26:33,321 --> 01:26:34,857
You take Kayo for it

1336
01:26:38,459 --> 01:26:40,564
I'll get the money

1337
01:26:50,738 --> 01:26:52,877
Where will you get
the money from?

1338
01:26:53,675 --> 01:26:55,552
An old friend

1339
01:26:59,280 --> 01:27:01,157
He owes me one

1340
01:27:02,183 --> 01:27:04,561
I'll call you when
I get the money

1341
01:27:10,592 --> 01:27:12,469
You just get Kayo to the ground

1342
01:27:14,762 --> 01:27:16,264
You're looking good

1343
01:27:39,721 --> 01:27:41,428
Rusy
- Yes Papa?

1344
01:27:43,791 --> 01:27:44,929
Give Kayo this tip

1345
01:27:45,326 --> 01:27:46,498
Yes?

1346
01:27:47,395 --> 01:27:48,567
When...

1347
01:27:49,964 --> 01:27:51,966
a bowler bowls...

1348
01:27:55,670 --> 01:27:57,843
Go on, Papa.
When a bowler bowls...

1349
01:27:58,273 --> 01:28:00,583
No, let him play
the way he does

1350
01:28:01,943 --> 01:28:04,389
He'll knock them off their feet

1351
01:28:31,339 --> 01:28:32,875
Everyone ready?
- Yes sir

1352
01:28:33,408 --> 01:28:35,649
Let's go.
Batsman to my right

1353
01:28:35,910 --> 01:28:37,480
Bowlers to my left

1354
01:29:03,004 --> 01:29:05,041
I want to meet
Dilip Dharmadhikari

1355
01:29:06,507 --> 01:29:07,611
Well?

1356
01:29:07,975 --> 01:29:11,650
From my club, at least
one boy should go to Lord's

1357
01:29:12,680 --> 01:29:13,784
You want your son to go?

1358
01:29:15,583 --> 01:29:16,960
He really wants to go

1359
01:29:17,352 --> 01:29:18,422
Do something

1360
01:29:19,020 --> 01:29:20,987
You do something
about those TV rights

1361
01:29:20,988 --> 01:29:22,490
Consider it done

1362
01:29:22,724 --> 01:29:24,533
Then consider this done, too

1363
01:29:26,327 --> 01:29:28,068
Gattu Godbole,
his name. RC Club

1364
01:29:28,596 --> 01:29:30,371
Gattu Godbole. OK

1365
01:29:32,500 --> 01:29:34,480
Excuse me, sir.
Mr. Deboo's here to meet you

1366
01:29:34,902 --> 01:29:36,848
Who Deboo?
- Behram Deboo

1367
01:29:40,775 --> 01:29:41,913
6th floor

1368
01:29:49,684 --> 01:29:50,662
Deboo

1369
01:29:58,493 --> 01:30:00,473
After so many years

1370
01:30:01,529 --> 01:30:03,031
Please sit down

1371
01:30:03,464 --> 01:30:05,842
You've put on some weight

1372
01:30:07,101 --> 01:30:08,842
What will you have?
Tea? Coffee?

1373
01:30:09,370 --> 01:30:11,475
Beer?

1374
01:30:11,906 --> 01:30:13,613
One coffee, please

1375
01:30:15,076 --> 01:30:16,943
How many years
has it been, Deboo?

1376
01:30:16,944 --> 01:30:18,048
38 years

1377
01:30:19,914 --> 01:30:21,791
How time flies

1378
01:30:24,652 --> 01:30:26,723
So, to what do I
owe this honor?

1379
01:30:29,390 --> 01:30:31,028
38 years back...

1380
01:30:32,427 --> 01:30:33,735
I had a friend

1381
01:30:35,863 --> 01:30:38,742
We did everything together...

1382
01:30:39,934 --> 01:30:41,743
shared all secrets...

1383
01:30:42,069 --> 01:30:46,711
checked out pretty girls together

1384
01:30:48,443 --> 01:30:53,392
We made thousands of runs
together in record partnerships

1385
01:30:53,714 --> 01:30:56,627
Those were the days

1386
01:31:00,588 --> 01:31:01,430
Dilip

1387
01:31:07,795 --> 01:31:11,038
What you did to me...

1388
01:31:11,866 --> 01:31:14,968
After 38 years, you're here
to make me feel guilty?

1389
01:31:14,969 --> 01:31:16,573
No
- Is that so?

1390
01:31:17,472 --> 01:31:19,577
Not at all

1391
01:31:20,741 --> 01:31:22,618
That's not so

1392
01:31:23,044 --> 01:31:25,524
I'm ready to forget and forgive

1393
01:31:26,647 --> 01:31:29,423
If I do that...

1394
01:31:30,184 --> 01:31:31,985
then you're my only friend

1395
01:31:31,986 --> 01:31:32,555
Yes

1396
01:31:32,787 --> 01:31:34,960
You are my friend, yes?
- Of course

1397
01:31:36,858 --> 01:31:37,836
Well?

1398
01:31:38,493 --> 01:31:39,062
Dilip

1399
01:31:40,027 --> 01:31:41,597
I have a grandson

1400
01:31:43,431 --> 01:31:45,911
Deboo, you're a grandfather?

1401
01:31:46,467 --> 01:31:48,003
I don't look old enough, I know

1402
01:31:49,904 --> 01:31:51,178
He's a cricketer

1403
01:31:51,606 --> 01:31:53,085
Of course he is

1404
01:31:53,608 --> 01:31:58,819
You know that
cricket camp at Lord's?

1405
01:31:59,747 --> 01:32:01,954
He wants to go for that

1406
01:32:04,785 --> 01:32:07,527
Well, you see, I must tell you...

1407
01:32:07,755 --> 01:32:09,666
the selection is based on merit

1408
01:32:09,891 --> 01:32:11,858
And in this position,
I can't favor anyone

1409
01:32:11,859 --> 01:32:12,803
Hold it, Dilip

1410
01:32:12,994 --> 01:32:15,497
I'm not asking you
to do anything wrong

1411
01:32:15,530 --> 01:32:16,565
I'm just clarifying

1412
01:32:17,131 --> 01:32:18,804
I understand your position

1413
01:32:18,933 --> 01:32:21,504
He's so good,
he will be selected

1414
01:32:22,103 --> 01:32:26,984
The problem is the Rs. 150,000
to be paid after that

1415
01:32:28,109 --> 01:32:30,953
It's 150,000 yes

1416
01:32:31,245 --> 01:32:33,816
So I thought of some options

1417
01:32:35,149 --> 01:32:37,720
Can you ask the Board...

1418
01:32:38,119 --> 01:32:41,931
for a grant or scholarship?

1419
01:32:42,189 --> 01:32:44,032
No, it will not work out

1420
01:32:44,725 --> 01:32:47,706
If we do it for one,
we'll have to do it for others

1421
01:32:47,828 --> 01:32:49,569
And if the Press gets wind of it...

1422
01:32:49,697 --> 01:32:50,573
I know

1423
01:32:50,765 --> 01:32:53,507
In this position, actually,
my hands are tied

1424
01:32:53,834 --> 01:32:55,142
I understand

1425
01:32:55,803 --> 01:32:56,873
What now...

1426
01:33:00,942 --> 01:33:04,253
There's another option

1427
01:33:08,516 --> 01:33:10,120
As my friend...

1428
01:33:12,286 --> 01:33:15,597
can't you loan me Rs. 150,0007

1429
01:33:24,131 --> 01:33:24,905
Yeah?

1430
01:33:25,833 --> 01:33:27,210
One moment

1431
01:33:31,806 --> 01:33:32,910
I'll just be back

1432
01:33:54,195 --> 01:33:55,674
Kayoze - Net no. 2

1433
01:34:06,107 --> 01:34:09,213
Every gaze is fixed on you

1434
01:34:09,810 --> 01:34:14,020
Each heart harbors new hope

1435
01:34:19,320 --> 01:34:22,130
The crowds support you

1436
01:34:22,757 --> 01:34:24,202
The crowds support you

1437
01:34:24,325 --> 01:34:26,026
So do what champions do

1438
01:34:26,027 --> 01:34:30,806
With a mighty bat,
make a hefty score

1439
01:34:30,998 --> 01:34:33,842
More...

1440
01:34:34,201 --> 01:34:35,236
He hits

1441
01:34:35,736 --> 01:34:36,771
Up and a way

1442
01:34:37,304 --> 01:34:38,977
In the air

1443
01:34:39,073 --> 01:34:40,677
A big hit

1444
01:34:55,156 --> 01:34:56,134
Thank you

1445
01:35:00,294 --> 01:35:01,932
Sir, he won't be back

1446
01:35:02,663 --> 01:35:03,300
Why?

1447
01:35:03,731 --> 01:35:05,039
I speak from experience

1448
01:35:10,871 --> 01:35:11,747
Sir

1449
01:35:13,374 --> 01:35:15,115
I'm a big fan

1450
01:35:15,910 --> 01:35:17,412
You took eight wickets...

1451
01:35:17,878 --> 01:35:19,858
on the dead pitch
of the Matunga Club

1452
01:35:21,015 --> 01:35:22,016
I still remember that clearly

1453
01:35:23,084 --> 01:35:28,124
Sir, an autograph please

1454
01:35:36,097 --> 01:35:38,008
Hello Papa? Any luck?

1455
01:35:39,200 --> 01:35:43,012
It'll work out, don't worry

1456
01:35:44,739 --> 01:35:46,878
How's our boy playing?

1457
01:35:49,944 --> 01:35:51,855
He's knocking them
off their feet

1458
01:35:53,447 --> 01:35:55,984
Papa, you went to meet
Dilip Dharmadhikari?

1459
01:35:58,686 --> 01:35:59,960
It didn't work out, did it, Papa?

1460
01:36:02,256 --> 01:36:04,236
It's ok Papa, we'll find a way

1461
01:36:05,192 --> 01:36:07,365
It'll work out, Papa.
Don't worry

1462
01:36:07,828 --> 01:36:09,933
Later... I'll call you later

1463
01:36:14,835 --> 01:36:16,337
Well played, Kayo

1464
01:36:18,339 --> 01:36:19,818
Nice

1465
01:36:20,241 --> 01:36:22,915
Sir, I have to leave
on some urgent work

1466
01:36:23,144 --> 01:36:25,181
Would you please
drop Kayo home?

1467
01:36:25,446 --> 01:36:26,754
Sure, no problem

1468
01:36:28,482 --> 01:36:30,086
Shot

1469
01:36:32,853 --> 01:36:34,025
Don't worry, I'll drop him

1470
01:36:35,422 --> 01:36:37,766
Get away from the car

1471
01:36:38,092 --> 01:36:39,503
Don't touch the car

1472
01:36:39,994 --> 01:36:41,473
Don't touch the hood

1473
01:36:41,896 --> 01:36:43,466
Everyone move back

1474
01:36:46,333 --> 01:36:48,279
Stop taking pictures

1475
01:36:52,506 --> 01:36:53,507
Who are you?

1476
01:36:53,908 --> 01:36:55,478
Rustom Behram Deboo,
Transport Office

1477
01:36:56,076 --> 01:36:58,283
So help me out here.
Move everyone away

1478
01:36:58,779 --> 01:37:00,190
Sir, I have an idea

1479
01:37:00,447 --> 01:37:01,391
There's Sachin

1480
01:37:01,849 --> 01:37:02,418
Where?

1481
01:37:02,449 --> 01:37:03,325
There

1482
01:37:06,053 --> 01:37:07,532
Sir, where are you off to?

1483
01:37:07,988 --> 01:37:08,898
To Sachin...

1484
01:37:08,989 --> 01:37:10,024
Sir, that was just to distract them

1485
01:37:10,191 --> 01:37:12,068
Before they're back,
put barricades here

1486
01:37:12,226 --> 01:37:15,036
I'll be back in ten minutes.
I have another idea

1487
01:37:15,296 --> 01:37:16,331
Thank you

1488
01:37:21,268 --> 01:37:22,406
Sir

1489
01:37:22,970 --> 01:37:24,381
Excuse me, sir

1490
01:37:25,039 --> 01:37:26,985
Sir, your scooter key

1491
01:37:27,208 --> 01:37:29,017
Thank you
- Mention not

1492
01:37:30,911 --> 01:37:33,414
Good news, old chap

1493
01:37:33,981 --> 01:37:36,018
No Ferrari has come
here for gas

1494
01:37:36,350 --> 01:37:38,151
In Mumbai, there are only
five gas stations...

1495
01:37:38,152 --> 01:37:39,426
that stock gas for the Ferrari

1496
01:37:39,854 --> 01:37:41,333
We've checked all five

1497
01:37:41,789 --> 01:37:42,859
This means...

1498
01:37:43,090 --> 01:37:47,004
the thief has gas for only 50 km

1499
01:37:47,294 --> 01:37:49,831
But 50 km in which direction?

1500
01:37:50,030 --> 01:37:52,374
The car may have gone
50 km this way...

1501
01:37:52,900 --> 01:37:55,244
while we go 50 km that way

1502
01:37:55,536 --> 01:37:57,573
That makes 100 km

1503
01:37:58,038 --> 01:38:01,076
Your brain measures
1 centimeter

1504
01:38:01,809 --> 01:38:03,447
Don't put a 100 km load on it

1505
01:38:03,577 --> 01:38:05,557
C'mon, start your Ferrari

1506
01:38:05,980 --> 01:38:08,392
My brain's not working

1507
01:38:08,449 --> 01:38:09,450
Give me the helmet

1508
01:38:10,284 --> 01:38:13,527
That scooter key looked like
the Ferrari key to me

1509
01:38:13,921 --> 01:38:15,559
Don't remind me of the key.
C'mon, hurry

1510
01:38:16,557 --> 01:38:18,400
And how much for this?

1511
01:38:18,492 --> 01:38:21,336
5000... 3000... 2000...

1512
01:38:21,528 --> 01:38:23,599
1500... 1500... 1500...

1513
01:38:24,031 --> 01:38:24,839
Rs. 1500...

1514
01:38:25,032 --> 01:38:27,012
What model, what size?

1515
01:38:27,301 --> 01:38:28,336
Tell me, Your Royal Highness?

1516
01:38:28,869 --> 01:38:31,349
Size... It's big

1517
01:38:32,072 --> 01:38:33,176
Is it a truck?

1518
01:38:33,841 --> 01:38:35,411
You need a large banner

1519
01:38:36,911 --> 01:38:37,514
Sorry

1520
01:38:38,846 --> 01:38:39,984
Excuse me

1521
01:38:40,447 --> 01:38:42,222
Sir

1522
01:38:42,583 --> 01:38:43,391
A banner

1523
01:38:43,584 --> 01:38:44,284
Banner?

1524
01:38:44,285 --> 01:38:45,286
Why a banner?

1525
01:39:10,344 --> 01:39:12,950
Lower it carefully

1526
01:39:13,314 --> 01:39:15,225
That's great

1527
01:39:16,450 --> 01:39:19,659
No one will touch it now

1528
01:39:38,605 --> 01:39:40,050
Clear off now

1529
01:39:40,607 --> 01:39:42,917
Sir, one moment

1530
01:39:44,278 --> 01:39:45,484
BCA?

1531
01:39:45,913 --> 01:39:47,290
Bombay Cricket Association?

1532
01:39:47,581 --> 01:39:49,618
Sir, I was once President

1533
01:39:49,984 --> 01:39:50,519
Of BCA?

1534
01:39:50,684 --> 01:39:52,391
No... Our BCA is...

1535
01:39:52,553 --> 01:39:53,657
Borivli Cricket Association

1536
01:39:54,054 --> 01:39:56,034
A cricket club for our constables

1537
01:39:56,223 --> 01:39:59,227
Sir, I'm famous for my
quarter centuries

1538
01:39:59,660 --> 01:40:03,005
Sir, you're here for
Sachin Tendulkar's car?

1539
01:40:07,267 --> 01:40:09,474
Who's the senior officer here?

1540
01:40:09,670 --> 01:40:12,173
Who brought Sachin's car here?

1541
01:40:13,040 --> 01:40:14,951
It wasn't me.
It was Inspector Mhatre

1542
01:40:14,975 --> 01:40:17,148
Get Inspector Mhatre

1543
01:40:18,012 --> 01:40:18,711
Get Mhatre here

1544
01:40:18,712 --> 01:40:20,692
Sir, Inspector Mhatre
plays football

1545
01:40:21,015 --> 01:40:23,017
He knows nothing of cricket

1546
01:40:23,183 --> 01:40:24,594
This is Sachin's car

1547
01:40:24,952 --> 01:40:26,124
He didn't know that

1548
01:40:26,253 --> 01:40:28,290
The car was in a
No Parking zone, so...

1549
01:40:28,555 --> 01:40:33,004
Yes, but how will I know if
the car's with cops or thieves?

1550
01:40:33,227 --> 01:40:34,331
It's like this, sir...

1551
01:40:34,495 --> 01:40:36,065
When we confiscate a car...

1552
01:40:36,330 --> 01:40:37,468
we make a chalk circle there

1553
01:40:37,698 --> 01:40:41,236
In it we write the name of
the police station the car is at

1554
01:40:41,368 --> 01:40:43,075
If you make a chalk mark...

1555
01:40:43,303 --> 01:40:45,442
and thousands walk over it...

1556
01:40:45,539 --> 01:40:47,246
won't it get erased?

1557
01:40:48,008 --> 01:40:51,310
Yes... But sir,
we have to follow orders

1558
01:40:51,311 --> 01:40:52,722
Who's the senior officer here?

1559
01:40:54,014 --> 01:40:55,084
Who's your senior?

1560
01:40:55,215 --> 01:40:56,216
I'm the senior-most, sir

1561
01:40:56,316 --> 01:40:58,023
But don't scold me sir, please

1562
01:40:58,218 --> 01:40:59,094
Did I scold you?

1563
01:40:59,486 --> 01:41:00,294
Did I get angry?

1564
01:41:00,587 --> 01:41:02,191
Did I raise my voice?
- No

1565
01:41:02,256 --> 01:41:03,701
Who dares to say
I scolded you?

1566
01:41:04,058 --> 01:41:05,992
I want to meet
your senior officer

1567
01:41:05,993 --> 01:41:07,995
Sir, take the car

1568
01:41:08,729 --> 01:41:11,073
Yes, take the car

1569
01:41:11,298 --> 01:41:13,073
I'll handle Inspector Mhatre

1570
01:41:13,267 --> 01:41:14,371
No fine, nothing

1571
01:41:14,501 --> 01:41:16,310
You must take the fine
- No sir

1572
01:41:16,470 --> 01:41:17,642
Sachin will scold me

1573
01:41:18,105 --> 01:41:20,051
Please sir,
I don't want anything

1574
01:41:20,240 --> 01:41:20,650
OK

1575
01:41:21,275 --> 01:41:23,414
But how do I take the car...

1576
01:41:23,544 --> 01:41:25,387
Sir, I'll get you a tow truck

1577
01:41:25,579 --> 01:41:27,581
It'll drop you where you want

1578
01:41:27,781 --> 01:41:30,227
Free of charge
- Totally free

1579
01:41:31,085 --> 01:41:32,792
Gautiya... Ashok...

1580
01:41:36,056 --> 01:41:36,534
Hello?

1581
01:41:36,623 --> 01:41:38,227
Hello Papa, this is Kayo

1582
01:41:38,592 --> 01:41:39,297
Yes son?

1583
01:41:39,493 --> 01:41:40,801
Papa, I got selected

1584
01:41:41,395 --> 01:41:42,669
I'm so proud of you, son

1585
01:41:43,130 --> 01:41:45,235
Kayo, listen - I got the money

1586
01:41:45,466 --> 01:41:46,342
Got the money?

1587
01:41:47,267 --> 01:41:47,608
Sir

1588
01:41:48,168 --> 01:41:48,771
One moment, sir

1589
01:41:49,136 --> 01:41:50,274
Papa, hold on

1590
01:41:51,071 --> 01:41:52,744
Sir, it's Papa.
He got the money

1591
01:41:53,674 --> 01:41:54,709
Rusy, congratulations

1592
01:41:55,175 --> 01:41:56,813
Today, both father and son
are victorious

1593
01:41:57,578 --> 01:41:58,318
Thank you, sir

1594
01:41:58,712 --> 01:41:59,486
Kayo sounds...

1595
01:42:00,047 --> 01:42:02,425
He's jumping with joy

1596
01:42:04,284 --> 01:42:07,128
Sir, I'll see you tomorrow
morning then

1597
01:42:07,321 --> 01:42:08,493
OK. Here, talk to him

1598
01:42:10,691 --> 01:42:12,432
Kayo listen
- Yes Papa?

1599
01:42:12,593 --> 01:42:14,300
I'll call you later

1600
01:42:14,595 --> 01:42:17,735
I'll call you.
I love you. Bye

1601
01:42:18,599 --> 01:42:20,545
Gautiya, let's go
- Gautiya, drive safe

1602
01:42:20,667 --> 01:42:22,271
Thank you, sir

1603
01:43:03,810 --> 01:43:06,120
What's wrong with Pakya?

1604
01:43:10,450 --> 01:43:13,192
Dad's here.
Give me the number plate

1605
01:43:18,358 --> 01:43:20,235
Whoever wants to take
a picture, take it now

1606
01:43:20,527 --> 01:43:24,236
Tomorrow's newspaper
should print this headline...

1607
01:43:24,431 --> 01:43:27,605
Politician's son commits suicide'

1608
01:43:28,168 --> 01:43:30,546
Pakya, what are you doing?

1609
01:43:30,704 --> 01:43:31,704
Get down

1610
01:43:31,705 --> 01:43:33,446
Yes, come down

1611
01:43:35,242 --> 01:43:37,153
At the wedding today,
I want the Ferrari

1612
01:43:37,544 --> 01:43:39,421
If the Ferrari is there...

1613
01:43:39,713 --> 01:43:41,215
I'll be there

1614
01:43:41,515 --> 01:43:43,188
If not, I'll go up there...

1615
01:43:43,317 --> 01:43:45,524
your vote bank
will go down there

1616
01:43:45,752 --> 01:43:47,390
Why are you doing this?

1617
01:43:47,688 --> 01:43:49,497
Get down. Come home

1618
01:43:49,623 --> 01:43:51,159
Mom, stop talking

1619
01:43:51,658 --> 01:43:53,262
You're talking too much

1620
01:43:53,393 --> 01:43:56,772
The People's Representative
is not talking at all

1621
01:43:57,231 --> 01:43:58,232
Lokre

1622
01:43:58,565 --> 01:44:00,772
Speak, o Savior of the Masses

1623
01:44:01,335 --> 01:44:03,337
You're so brave, aren't you?

1624
01:44:03,503 --> 01:44:05,540
OK, go ahead and jump

1625
01:44:05,739 --> 01:44:08,345
Jump or I'll shoot you, Pakya

1626
01:44:08,609 --> 01:44:09,883
Dad's going to shoot me, man

1627
