C'mon, let's donate this

1891
01:57:32,111 --> 01:57:38,585
Peace and Wealth breeze in,
Suffering beats a retreat

1892
01:57:38,651 --> 01:57:39,356
The Ferrari

1893
01:57:39,419 --> 01:57:40,056
Ferrari

1894
01:57:41,487 --> 01:57:42,693
The Ferrari!

1895
01:57:43,022 --> 01:57:44,558
It's the Ferrari, yes

1896
01:57:44,590 --> 01:57:46,069
Mohan, this way

1897
01:57:46,092 --> 01:57:47,196
Hurry

1898
01:57:48,194 --> 01:57:49,434
Pakya

1899
01:57:50,196 --> 01:57:51,266
Get back inside

1900
01:57:56,035 --> 01:57:57,402
Found our Ferrari

1901
01:57:57,403 --> 01:57:58,677
Where?
- There, ahead

1902
01:57:58,771 --> 01:57:59,647
What happened?

1903
01:58:00,406 --> 01:58:01,350
I don't know

1904
01:58:01,574 --> 01:58:03,110
The Ferrari stopped

1905
01:58:04,010 --> 01:58:05,580
Maybe the carburetor is clogged

1906
01:58:05,611 --> 01:58:07,750
Go check it, quick

1907
01:58:08,114 --> 01:58:09,347
Open the hood

1908
01:58:09,348 --> 01:58:10,549
Which button do I press?

1909
01:58:10,550 --> 01:58:11,722
Press all the buttons

1910
01:58:13,186 --> 01:58:14,494
It's open

1911
01:58:15,221 --> 01:58:16,063
Pakya

1912
01:58:16,122 --> 01:58:16,623
What?

1913
01:58:16,756 --> 01:58:17,791
The engine fell out

1914
01:58:18,057 --> 01:58:18,535
What?

1915
01:58:20,693 --> 01:58:22,570
There's no hole underneath

1916
01:58:23,062 --> 01:58:24,097
How did it fall out?

1917
01:58:24,163 --> 01:58:24,664
Back off

1918
01:58:26,132 --> 01:58:27,509
Mohan

1919
01:58:27,700 --> 01:58:29,111
The engine's gone

1920
01:58:29,335 --> 01:58:32,578
The engine's in
Shamshu's furnace

1921
01:58:32,705 --> 01:58:34,651
This car's engine is
in the back, you blockhead

1922
01:58:34,807 --> 01:58:36,047
Look in the back

1923
01:58:37,677 --> 01:58:39,384
Pakya, the engine's here

1924
01:58:39,512 --> 01:58:41,617
The engine is safe
in a glass box

1925
01:58:42,115 --> 01:58:44,618
You. How did you know
the engine was in the back?

1926
01:58:44,784 --> 01:58:46,525
This is our boss's car

1927
01:58:46,552 --> 01:58:48,759
We also own an Alto, a Scorpio...

1928
01:58:48,788 --> 01:58:51,098
Tell him, Mohan
- Right

1929
01:58:51,257 --> 01:58:52,759
This is our boss's car.
Move away

1930
01:58:52,825 --> 01:58:54,498
If it's your boss's car...

1931
01:58:54,527 --> 01:58:56,404
tell me why it has stalled

1932
01:58:56,562 --> 01:58:58,098
Well, you see...

1933
01:58:58,264 --> 01:58:59,641
But why should I tell you?

1934
01:58:59,799 --> 01:59:02,075
Yes, who're you to ask?
Move aside

1935
01:59:02,201 --> 01:59:04,374
Go, Head of Security
- Take out the gun

1936
01:59:06,739 --> 01:59:07,717
What's wrong with the car?

1937
01:59:08,441 --> 01:59:11,354
The car's run out of gas

1938
01:59:11,511 --> 01:59:12,251
Now what?

1939
01:59:13,246 --> 01:59:14,452
Let's take gas from that scooter

1940
01:59:15,214 --> 01:59:17,626
Take gas from the scooter,
put it into the car

1941
01:59:17,717 --> 01:59:19,287
It's like this...

1942
01:59:19,619 --> 01:59:22,122
You don't put regular gas
into a Ferrari

1943
01:59:22,355 --> 01:59:24,096
A special kind goes into it

1944
01:59:24,257 --> 01:59:27,670
And only we know
where to get it

1945
01:59:33,332 --> 01:59:34,242
Listen up

1946
01:59:34,300 --> 01:59:35,745
Pakya
- Quiet

1947
01:59:36,102 --> 01:59:38,673
Look, I need your help

1948
01:59:39,405 --> 01:59:40,748
This is your boss's Ferrari?

1949
01:59:40,806 --> 01:59:42,683
Get me to my wedding
in this Ferrari

1950
01:59:42,808 --> 01:59:44,754
Once I get there...

1951
01:59:44,877 --> 01:59:48,381
the car's yours.
You can take it back

1952
01:59:48,748 --> 01:59:52,321
If you don't help me,
then this engine...

1953
01:59:52,385 --> 01:59:54,456
No, don't

1954
01:59:54,554 --> 01:59:55,897
How will we get him there?

1955
01:59:56,155 --> 01:59:57,691
The Ferrari is out of gas

1956
01:59:58,558 --> 01:59:59,332
Well?

1957
01:59:59,625 --> 02:00:03,368
The trials of life...

1958
02:00:04,864 --> 02:00:06,468
I have an idea

1959
02:00:07,200 --> 02:00:09,544
are eased by the Lord

1960
02:00:09,802 --> 02:00:12,681
Mohan, how much
farther is the gas station?

1961
02:00:12,838 --> 02:00:14,818
Why don't you take
the bullock's place?

1962
02:00:15,174 --> 02:00:16,244
We may reach faster

1963
02:00:17,476 --> 02:00:19,285
Any fractures?
- No sir

1964
02:00:42,902 --> 02:00:44,939
Hello, Uncle Pesi?
Rusy here

1965
02:00:45,304 --> 02:00:50,413
Could you please check on
Kayo at my house?

1966
02:00:50,710 --> 02:00:52,189
He's not answering the phone

1967
02:00:52,311 --> 02:00:52,880
Thank you

1968
02:01:01,554 --> 02:01:02,430
He looks fine

1969
02:01:02,722 --> 02:01:04,963
Let's get a CT scan
- OK sir

1970
02:01:08,628 --> 02:01:10,767
Rusy, Kayo is nowhere

1971
02:01:11,364 --> 02:01:11,967
You come home quick

1972
02:01:12,298 --> 02:01:15,336
Those goons were hanging
around for a long time

1973
02:01:29,849 --> 02:01:31,260
Kayo

1974
02:01:33,386 --> 02:01:35,229
Kayo

1975
02:01:40,493 --> 02:01:43,269
Rusy, where're you going?
- They're dangerous guys

1976
02:01:44,230 --> 02:01:51,876
The dawn of auspicious days

1977
02:01:53,739 --> 02:01:57,243
Welcome, my friends
from the Press

1978
02:01:57,610 --> 02:02:02,855
Today, I give 201 couples
a loan-free life

1979
02:02:03,015 --> 02:02:04,824
No. 176 - Please come here

1980
02:02:05,418 --> 02:02:08,456
Of these, 200 are my social work

1981
02:02:08,921 --> 02:02:12,459
And 1 is my homework

1982
02:02:12,758 --> 02:02:13,736
My son Pakya

1983
02:02:16,962 --> 02:02:18,373
The Ferrari

1984
02:02:20,366 --> 02:02:23,040
Prakash Mandke, No. 201

1985
02:02:23,536 --> 02:02:24,869
That brings me to the end...

1986
02:02:24,870 --> 02:02:26,907
TV crews
- Long live India

1987
02:02:27,006 --> 02:02:29,607
Here, look here

1988
02:02:29,608 --> 02:02:31,849
Here
- What's happening?

1989
02:02:32,345 --> 02:02:33,551
Hit it

1990
02:02:34,680 --> 02:02:35,784
I will show you...

1991
02:02:35,948 --> 02:02:38,622
I will give you Breaking News

1992
02:02:38,951 --> 02:02:40,430
Here a Pakya...

1993
02:02:40,820 --> 02:02:42,458
there a Pakya

1994
02:02:42,588 --> 02:02:46,458
Reporters, tell me
how many Pakyas?

1995
02:02:46,459 --> 02:02:47,597
So who's the real Pakya?

1996
02:02:47,626 --> 02:02:49,333
Follow me

1997
02:02:50,296 --> 02:02:52,071
You see this groom?

1998
02:02:52,398 --> 02:02:55,379
Now see my dad's social work

1999
02:02:55,468 --> 02:02:56,469
Look at this

2000
02:02:58,971 --> 02:02:59,676
Grandpa

2001
02:02:59,839 --> 02:03:01,648
His grandson is older than me

2002
02:03:02,475 --> 02:03:04,887
That concludes
what I had to say...

2003
02:03:05,344 --> 02:03:06,084
Oh no you don't

2004
02:03:08,414 --> 02:03:09,586
Who's this 201 ?

2005
02:03:09,782 --> 02:03:11,455
C'mon 201 , lift your veil

2006
02:03:11,650 --> 02:03:12,685
Show yourself

2007
02:03:12,818 --> 02:03:14,491
What is this?
- Melodrama

2008
02:03:14,653 --> 02:03:17,532
I've learnt from what
I've seen since childhood

2009
02:03:19,024 --> 02:03:20,094
Should I shoot?

2010
02:03:20,359 --> 02:03:21,770
Aren't these your words?

2011
02:03:21,827 --> 02:03:22,965
1...

2012
02:03:23,462 --> 02:03:25,601
Should I shoot... 2...

2013
02:03:26,065 --> 02:03:27,908
Should I shoot? Take this

2014
02:03:28,701 --> 02:03:30,476
What're you doing, son?

2015
02:03:30,770 --> 02:03:31,874
Watch it

2016
02:03:32,037 --> 02:03:33,846
It's Babbu didi

2017
02:03:36,942 --> 02:03:39,821
Dad's made
laughing stock of you too

2018
02:03:40,946 --> 02:03:42,357
Pakya, where's my son?

2019
02:03:42,615 --> 02:03:43,787
Look, his son's also missing

2020
02:03:49,054 --> 02:03:50,055
Babbu didi?

2021
02:03:54,460 --> 02:03:55,029
Pakya

2022
02:03:55,394 --> 02:03:57,431
Tell me where my son is,
or I'll shoot

2023
02:03:57,496 --> 02:03:59,635
Tell me

2024
02:04:00,366 --> 02:04:02,573
Mom, I don't know
where his son is

2025
02:04:02,601 --> 02:04:04,478
My son would never do that

2026
02:04:04,603 --> 02:04:06,640
He would never kidnap
someone's child

2027
02:04:06,705 --> 02:04:08,685
Rusy, wait

2028
02:04:08,774 --> 02:04:09,946
Where's his son?

2029
02:04:10,009 --> 02:04:11,955
I swear I don't know.
Ask them

2030
02:04:12,011 --> 02:04:13,649
Where's his son?

2031
02:04:13,712 --> 02:04:15,953
When we left, he was
running towards the sea

2032
02:04:16,081 --> 02:04:17,685
And he was crying

2033
02:04:19,084 --> 02:04:22,395
Mom, this guy stole the Ferrari

2034
02:04:22,588 --> 02:04:24,067
His son got to know

2035
02:04:24,490 --> 02:04:27,960
I think he's gone towards
the sea to commit suicide

2036
02:04:27,993 --> 02:04:29,097
Be quiet

2037
02:04:31,030 --> 02:04:33,738
Suicide? Your son's
committed suicide?

2038
02:04:36,769 --> 02:04:39,579
You've lost your son.
How do you feel?

2039
02:04:39,738 --> 02:04:41,547
Do you think he killed himself?

2040
02:04:41,674 --> 02:04:43,711
Where must he be?
- What happened, sir?

2041
02:04:44,043 --> 02:04:48,014
Where is your son?
What is your answer?

2042
02:04:52,751 --> 02:04:53,422
Everyone look here

2043
02:04:53,486 --> 02:04:56,626
If you live near the beach,
please come out of your home

2044
02:04:56,789 --> 02:04:58,063
Please rush to the beach

2045
02:04:58,190 --> 02:05:00,466
If you see a child running,
please stop him

2046
02:05:00,526 --> 02:05:01,766
He's my son, Kayo

2047
02:05:02,061 --> 02:05:03,597
He runs very fast

2048
02:05:03,829 --> 02:05:06,207
Don't let him go near the water

2049
02:05:07,066 --> 02:05:09,137
Not into the sea

2050
02:05:12,605 --> 02:05:14,585
My son's this high

2051
02:05:14,740 --> 02:05:16,151
4 feet, 9 inches

2052
02:05:16,575 --> 02:05:18,782
Dusky skin

2053
02:05:19,545 --> 02:05:20,683
This is him

2054
02:05:21,480 --> 02:05:22,686
He's always smiling

2055
02:05:23,516 --> 02:05:26,986
Kayoze Rustom Deboo.
His full name

2056
02:05:29,788 --> 02:05:31,734
Kayo, I didn't know what to do

2057
02:05:32,858 --> 02:05:34,496
Couldn't get a loan from work

2058
02:05:34,793 --> 02:05:36,795
The bank refused me a loan

2059
02:05:37,596 --> 02:05:39,473
I didn't mean to steal, Kayo

2060
02:05:40,766 --> 02:05:42,768
I made a mistake

2061
02:05:44,970 --> 02:05:46,711
Grandpa is right

2062
02:05:47,740 --> 02:05:50,152
We shouldn't dream at all

2063
02:05:52,478 --> 02:05:56,085
Please give me back my Kayo.
I can't live without him

2064
02:05:57,983 --> 02:06:01,556
If you want to Contact me,
call me on my phone...

2065
02:06:04,957 --> 02:06:07,198
Listen, you guys
search Girgaum beach

2066
02:06:07,493 --> 02:06:08,938
I'll check Dadar and Juhu beach

2067
02:06:09,762 --> 02:06:12,504
Keep in touch with me.
Call me every 5 minutes

2068
02:06:13,032 --> 02:06:14,807
I'm just leaving home...

2069
02:06:16,535 --> 02:06:18,208
I'll call you back

2070
02:06:20,205 --> 02:06:22,048
Kayo, where have you been?

2071
02:06:24,543 --> 02:06:26,113
Sir, Papa...

2072
02:06:28,614 --> 02:06:33,256
Sir, the police will take
Papa away. Please help me

2073
02:06:34,653 --> 02:06:36,291
Whoever finds my son
can have my apartment

2074
02:06:36,589 --> 02:06:38,923
It has one bedroom
and a large living room

2075
02:06:38,924 --> 02:06:40,992
Just find my son please

2076
02:06:40,993 --> 02:06:41,869
Rusy?

2077
02:06:41,961 --> 02:06:44,840
Please help me

2078
02:06:47,166 --> 02:06:47,871
Hello?

2079
02:06:48,000 --> 02:06:49,707
Rusy

2080
02:06:53,572 --> 02:06:55,848
Papa, Kayo's gone

2081
02:06:56,675 --> 02:06:58,712
Kayo's gone

2082
02:06:59,912 --> 02:07:00,890
Papa

2083
02:07:05,184 --> 02:07:06,094
Papa

2084
02:07:08,153 --> 02:07:09,564
Kayo

2085
02:07:11,090 --> 02:07:12,330
Where were you?

2086
02:07:21,800 --> 02:07:23,040
I'm sorry, son

2087
02:07:32,344 --> 02:07:33,823
I'm sorry, Kayo

2088
02:07:36,015 --> 02:07:39,053
I'm really sorry,
I shouldn't have done it

2089
02:07:39,752 --> 02:07:43,029
If I don't go to Lord's,
you think I won't play cricket?

2090
02:07:46,992 --> 02:07:49,370
I have the world's best coach

2091
02:07:50,062 --> 02:07:51,769
He'll train me

2092
02:07:52,331 --> 02:07:55,073
And you know, Sachin
didn't train at Lord's

2093
02:07:55,601 --> 02:07:57,740
He trained right here,
at Shivaji Park

2094
02:07:57,970 --> 02:07:59,347
And became the No. 1 cricketer

2095
02:07:59,772 --> 02:08:00,910
I'll be No. 1 too

2096
02:08:01,640 --> 02:08:02,846
100 centuries

2097
02:08:05,978 --> 02:08:08,219
Don't be upset, Papa

2098
02:08:08,847 --> 02:08:10,258
C'mon, be a good boy

2099
02:08:13,752 --> 02:08:16,062
Tomorrow, if I tell you
I want to go to the moon...

2100
02:08:16,255 --> 02:08:18,132
will you steal a spaceship
from NASA?

2101
02:08:19,024 --> 02:08:20,833
You understand, Papa?

2102
02:08:22,261 --> 02:08:24,969
I understand, Kayo

2103
02:08:25,998 --> 02:08:28,103
Now you'll say -
Look at the brighter side of life

2104
02:08:28,267 --> 02:08:29,211
Actually yes, Papa

2105
02:08:29,334 --> 02:08:31,905
If I'd gone to Lord's,
I would have gone alone

2106
02:08:32,337 --> 02:08:34,010
When I'm selected
for the Indian team...

2107
02:08:34,139 --> 02:08:35,846
I'll take you with me

2108
02:08:36,108 --> 02:08:37,815
I'll tell the Cricket Board clearly...

2109
02:08:37,876 --> 02:08:40,914
If you want Kayo in the team,
you have to take Papa along

2110
02:08:41,180 --> 02:08:42,955
I can't sleep without you

2111
02:08:43,148 --> 02:08:45,685
And who will wake me
for the match in the morning?

2112
02:08:47,686 --> 02:08:48,994
My Kayo's grown up

2113
02:08:50,856 --> 02:08:52,301
Grown up too soon

2114
02:08:55,728 --> 02:08:57,765
The flight has landed

2115
02:08:58,263 --> 02:08:59,708
Boss is back

2116
02:09:03,202 --> 02:09:05,182
Sorry, but can you
please hurry up?

2117
02:09:05,938 --> 02:09:08,316
Our boss's flight has landed

2118
02:09:08,941 --> 02:09:12,684
We have to take the Ferrari back

2119
02:09:23,255 --> 02:09:26,099
Babbu didi,
please return this money

2120
02:09:28,160 --> 02:09:29,798
Pakya, could you...

2121
02:09:32,765 --> 02:09:33,368
Thank you

2122
02:09:36,168 --> 02:09:37,078
The key, sir

2123
02:09:39,238 --> 02:09:40,478
Please forgive me

2124
02:09:40,873 --> 02:09:43,854
I must ask Sachin
for forgiveness too

2125
02:09:44,143 --> 02:09:46,180
Not today, sir.
We'll handle it from here

2126
02:09:46,411 --> 02:09:47,822
Meet him another day

2127
02:09:47,980 --> 02:09:50,085
You can take a photo
with him too

2128
02:09:50,215 --> 02:09:53,253
Yes. Sorry, got to rush now

2129
02:10:04,429 --> 02:10:05,464
Yes, I'll open it

2130
02:10:06,098 --> 02:10:08,044
Pandey, Boss not back yet?

2131
02:10:08,200 --> 02:10:09,042
Boss is back

2132
02:10:09,401 --> 02:10:10,880
When?
- Right now

2133
02:10:11,470 --> 02:10:12,949
Open it, quick

2134
02:10:28,520 --> 02:10:32,491
Please don't tell anyone
I gave out the Ferrari key

2135
02:10:32,991 --> 02:10:35,369
Please don't tell anyone
that I opened the gate

2136
02:10:35,527 --> 02:10:37,438
I would've lost my
status in the village

2137
02:10:37,830 --> 02:10:39,468
Saved
- Don't worry

2138
02:10:42,000 --> 02:10:43,001
Well done

2139
02:10:48,540 --> 02:10:49,416
Kayo

2140
02:10:50,475 --> 02:10:52,113
You know something?

2141
02:10:53,178 --> 02:10:57,422
You put a ball into a sock
and kept knocking it

2142
02:10:57,883 --> 02:11:01,023
That really irritated me

2143
02:11:02,354 --> 02:11:04,027
Now throw away that rotting sock

2144
02:11:04,223 --> 02:11:06,965
I'll come to the nets.
I will train you

2145
02:11:07,893 --> 02:11:10,430
You will play for India

2146
02:11:10,796 --> 02:11:12,901
You don't need to
go to London

2147
02:11:13,165 --> 02:11:14,940
Those players
should come here

2148
02:11:15,100 --> 02:11:16,579
We could teach
them a thing or two

2149
02:11:19,071 --> 02:11:21,017
Stop here

2150
02:11:22,241 --> 02:11:24,075
C'mon little one,
give me a hand

2151
02:11:24,076 --> 02:11:25,578
Who are these people?

2152
02:11:30,015 --> 02:11:32,518
Uncle Rusy, put Rs. 50 in this

2153
02:11:34,152 --> 02:11:36,564
There you go

2154
02:11:37,956 --> 02:11:39,435
It's done

2155
02:11:41,026 --> 02:11:44,872
We'd collected Rs.149,950

2156
02:11:45,130 --> 02:11:48,976
Now we have the complete
amount of 150,000

2157
02:11:51,169 --> 02:11:52,341
This is for you

2158
02:11:52,537 --> 02:11:53,914
But what is all this?

2159
02:11:54,139 --> 02:11:58,451
Rusy, our Kayo will
go to London now

2160
02:11:59,011 --> 02:12:00,354
Uncle Rusy...

2161
02:12:00,479 --> 02:12:02,925
this lady contributed
the largest bundle

2162
02:12:03,181 --> 02:12:04,387
Come on up

